## Permissions (Tauri v2)

Permissions are defined in `src-tauri/capabilities/default.json`:

```json
{
    "$schema": "...",
    "identifier": "default",
    "description": "Default permissions",
    "windows": ["main"],
    "permissions": [
        "core:default",
        "core:event:default",
        "shell:allow-open"
    ]
}
```

### Custom Permissions

```json
{
    "identifier": "custom-permission",
    "windows": ["main"],
    "permissions": [
        "core:default",
        {
            "identifier": "my-plugin:allow-do-something",
            "allow": [{ "path": "$APPDATA/**" }]
        }
    ]
}
```

