## Window Management

```typescript
import { getCurrentWindow } from '@tauri-apps/api/window';

const window = getCurrentWindow();

// Minimize
await window.minimize();

// Maximize/unmaximize
await window.toggleMaximize();

// Set title
await window.setTitle('New Title');

// Close
await window.close();
```

