## Rust Integration Pattern (Enterprise Orchestration)

This project uses a multi-crate architecture:

```
crates/desktop-core/  → Tauri integration layer
crates/control-server/ → Embedded Axum HTTP server
crates/domain/        → Shared types
crates/orchestrator/  → Workflow execution engine
```

### Command Routing Pattern

```rust
// In desktop-core/src/lib.rs
#[tauri::command]
async fn run_workflow(
    app: tauri::AppHandle,
    workflow_id: String,
) -> Result<String, String> {
    let orchestrator = app.state::<OrchestratorHandle>();
    orchestrator.run(workflow_id).await.map_err(|e| e.to_string())
}
```

